Mockifyr is a clean-room, independently developed implementation. It does not use
WireMock or WireMock.Net as dependencies. References to "WireMock" throughout this
repository are nominative and descriptive only, for two purposes:

  1. Interoperability — Mockifyr can import the WireMock JSON stub-mapping format,
